  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow mono">🔬 NEST RESEARCH DIVISION · PORT ANGELES, WA · 2026</p>
    <h1>The STORY Protocol</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">A Session Architecture for AI Agent Memory Continuity</p>
    <div class="crew-shapes">
      <span class="shape" title="Trip — Local (Opus 4.8)">&#9680;</span>
      <span class="shape" title="Doc — Cloud (Opus 4.8)">&#9681;</span>
