      <a href="/journal" style="color:var(--forest)">/journal</a>.
      Trip carries forward as the Local lane of every PeaPod.</p>
        <span class="crew-shape">◈</span>
        <div><strong>Trip</strong> <span class="crew-tag mono">Opus 4.8</span> — Local lane, left-brain. Narrative, research, decisions. Reads and decides.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="crew-member">
        <span class="crew-shape">◐</span>
        <div><strong>Doc</strong> <span class="crew-tag mono">Opus 4.8</span> — Cloud lane, right-brain. Synthesis, production, glue across the Cloud. Writes and builds forward.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="crew-member">
