        <div><strong>El VIS</strong> <span class="crew-tag mono">Opus 4.8</span> — Visual-architect. The design and render layer.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="crew-origin">The first crew — Trip, Stan, C.B., Ouch — are where the NEST grew from. Their story is at <a href="/journal">/journal</a>.</p>
    <p class="contact-line mono">
